{
  "stem": "11882.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They kept out until the Nuremberg trials got out, I guess.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But anyway, they came back slowly to Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nuremberg, as a city, rebuilt itself slowly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the trial people-- the Army, the U.S.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Army was very kind to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could always get an order, say, if you had time, which I practically never had, because Dr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kempner was a workaholic, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, he worked night and day, carrying great armfuls of documents home at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And had a big staff working for him in his office-- I don't know, a great big staff of lawyers, and research people, and translators, and so forth in his office.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the big trial, when he assisted Justice Jackson, he became a-- on the-- went to the staff of Telford Taylor, who was in charge-- General Telford Taylor was our wonderful director for the entire 12 subsequent proceedings.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jackson left-- he went home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kempner was mainly in charge of this trial of the ministries, the big government officials.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were 12 trials all together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He helped on some of the other trials to some extent, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as a man who had been in German government, and had, of course, native German, a German lawyer also, he could help lots of them-- lots of the American lawyers, also, with advice, or help, or finding a document that would help them, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on our spare time, we would go to Garmisch-Partenkirchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or wonderful-- we would go to Czechoslovakia, where Americans were loved.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, Czechoslovakia more or less, was an American foundation after World War I, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Czechs had been exiles in Pittsburgh, more or less, for the time during World War II when there was no is no more Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
